# Source documents are NEVER tracked in git.
# Distribution to members happens via Google Drive (see docs/DRIVE-SETUP.md),
# never via this public repo. Even fund-level docs (which are technically
# already in the encrypted dashboard data) shouldn't be in clear text here.
docs/source/**/*.pdf
docs/source/**/*.PDF
docs/source/**/*.doc
docs/source/**/*.docx
docs/source/**/*.xlsx
docs/source/**/*.xls
docs/source/**/*.csv
